name: Harhmix
description:
• Harhmix is a merge model which focus on anime style painting. it could also generate NSFW content.

  • Features and improvements of Version 4 (My individual opinion):

    • Improvement of shade

    • Improvement of background

    • Better or worse hands

  • How to use:

    • Clip: skip 2 or 1, In general, skip 1 is good at composition, but skip 2 is more creative.

    • VAE: Anything V3 VAE works very well, but other VAEs are triable.

    • Tags: Danbooru tag.

    • Negative prompts: Version 4 have no general negative prompts, now I use "(worst quality, low quality:1.4), bad eyebrow, fused eyebrow, bad teeth, poor drawn face" and change it depending on situations.

    • CFG: 7~11 is what I used in mostly time, lower CFG prone to Anything style, higher CFG prone to pastel-mix.

    • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras, Euler A perform better.

    • Highres fix: I perfer 20 steps and 0.45~0.65 Denoising strength.

      • Latent: Best performace but unstable.

      • R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B: Stable but nomal performace

  • List of merge source(Version 4): I only show the main merge source because of too many models and lora.

    • Anything-V3

    • Nutmegmix

    • AbyssOrangeMix2_hard

    • MIX-Pro-V3

    • Grapefruit

    • Novelai

    • Gape60

    • Sun and Shadow

    • Better light

    • Howls Moving Castle , Interior / Scenery LoRA ( Ghibli Style ) v3
